    "en": {
      "title": "Two Indian nationals arrested at Katunayake airport",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Customs officials have said that they have arrested two Indian nationals at the Katunayake airport.",
        "Customs officials at Katunayake Airport said that the said duo were arrested on their arrival in the country with gold and foreign currency worth Rs 19 crore.",
        "Officials of the Customs Department said that they are keeping the two Indian nationals at the Kattunayake airport and conducting further investigations."
      ],
